      <para id="id209071">Since <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mi>e</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo>≈</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math>, we approximate <emphasis effect="italics">X</emphasis> for values up to 4
and <emphasis effect="italics">Y</emphasis> for values up to 6.
</para>
